{"tid":1628580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"世柒：唔好搞Starbucks","createTime":"2019-10-06T03:40:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T13:39:42.000Z","uid":8478,"like":10,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2f593a6ef17fb451b9982b0ca862b39eac06e0fe","tid":1628580,"uid":8478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:40:30.000Z","msg":"暫時停止針對Starbucks，可以罷飲，可以搵人寫信去美國總公司，要求終止喺香港嘅專利權，但唔好攻擊，因為五毛可以Spin，始終香港人權及民主法未過，而Starbucks係數一數二嘅美國公司，所以暫停攻擊Starbucks係合理。至於元気系嘅壽司餐廳，要做好多文宣，最終迫日本元気總公司同美心終止協議。我個人咁睇，如果迫到伍家將美心餘下股權，全 部賣俾英資怡和集團，咁就可以結束行動。伍家必須為伍淑清為咗自己喺中國飛機餐生意而賣港，付出應付代價，呢個係基本原則。美心變成英資財團，反而會少好多日後喺香港存在嘅問題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://martinoei.com/article/29115/星期日戰略：-勇武-嘅戰略/amp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmartinoei.com%2Farticle%2F29115%2F%E6%98%9F%E6%9C%9F%E6%97%A5%E6%88%B0%E7%95%A5%EF%BC%9A-%E5%8B%87%E6%AD%A6-%E5%98%85%E6%88%B0%E7%95%A5%2Famp&d=15TDSCYqMG0%2FxcOE0oxfELhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=ba2f04b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://martinoei.com/article/29115/星期日戰略：-勇武-嘅戰略/amp</a><br />\n<br />\n我覺得最少好似搞完元氣咁 解釋返<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc71cd17d0a494c353491b8089eac42c99f708e7","tid":1628580,"uid":213747,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:43:09.000Z","msg":"佢講到咁理想 都要怡和或者其他英資肯買先得架<br />\n不過同意紅鋪未至於要裝修 <br />\n罷食或者最盡噴門口就夠"},{"pid":"a00596863454c59c9f5ea2a5fff6263c3dccf913","tid":1628580,"uid":157891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:45:15.000Z","msg":"認同"},{"pid":"0998cd6332b7af667c28421c4cb5d9ee7eae2b05","tid":1628580,"uid":8478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:48:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f100b7e5d3a97b99cfb687b2e171436f38bb8c76","tid":1628580,"uid":33714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc